-- Fed backs efforts to find funding for AIG: official
-- 
-- Mon Sep 15, 2008 5:07pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/15/us-aig-fed-funds-idUSWAT01005820080915

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - The Federal Reserve is supportive of efforts by Goldman Sachs and JPMorgan to raise funds for embattled insurer American International Group Inc, a Fed official said on Monday. 

 "The Fed is encouraging the parties to work this out and is supportive of efforts by these companies to find funding for AIG," the official said. (Reporting by  Mark Felsenthal )